HEADWORD: Parauque
<hw>Pa*rauque"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>A bird (<spn>Nyctidromus albicollis</spn>) ranging from Texas to
South America. It is allied to the night hawk and goatsucker.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

